data.description: Country living!  4 bedroom, 2 bath home on over half an acre in Belvidere NC.  The home has a living/dining combination, den with FP, large front porch, attached carport, plus a large sunroom addition (not included in the heated square footage). Huge yard has plenty of room for playing, gardening, and hobbies. Much work is needed to bring this home back to it's former glory.  Old singlewide with no value sets to the left of this home.
